          "_name": "services2",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"services2\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <!---->\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Sus\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"9\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Jos\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n        <!---->\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Arată titlu\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Arată sub-titlu\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Subtitle 2\" name=\"showSubtitle2\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Arată Butoane\" name=\"showButtons\" checked>\n        <select title=\"Align Buttons:\" name=\"alignBtn\" condition=\"showButtons\">\n            <option value=\"1\" selected>Left</option>\n            <option value=\"2\">Center</option>\n            <option value=\"3\">Right</option>\n        </select>\n        <!---->\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Media în Stînga/Dreapta\" name=\"reverseContent\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Dimensiune media\" name=\"mediaSize\" min=\"20\" max=\"80\" step=\"5\" value=\"50\">\n        <!---->\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Imagine de fundal\" value=\"../_images/background2.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Culoare de fundal\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video de fundal\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uNCr7NdOJgw\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Suprapunere\" name=\"overlay\" checked condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Culoare de suprapunere\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacitate\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <!---->\n    <!--Overlay-->\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n    <!--Container-->\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"col-md-12\">\n            <div class=\"media-container-row\">\n                <div class=\"mbr-figure\" mbr-style=\"{'width': mediaSize + '%'}\">\n                    <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/ac75068-952x711.jpeg\" alt=\"Mobirise\" title>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"align-left aside-content\">\n                    <h2 class=\"mbr-title pt-2 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">Set trenulete 80 piese My Busy Train din lemn</h2>\n                    <div class=\"mbr-section-text\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text text1 pt-2 mbr-light mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".text1\">Setul are 80 de piese din lemn de fag Canadian de cea mai buna caliatate si contine:&nbsp;<br>Un set de sine de diferite forme si lungimi \n<br>Pod suspendat \n<br>Un set vagon cu locomotive la ambele capete \n<br>Locomotiva cu doua vagoane \n<br>Semafor,  Masinuta, Indicatoare , Braduleti, Figurine...etc. \n<br>Imprimat colorat cu trasee auto<br>Setul contine instructiuni de asamblare detaliate, pas cu pas \n<br>Dimensiuni produs: 62 x 83 x 14 cm \n<br>Dimensiuni cutie ambalaj: 42 x 28 x 7,5 cm&nbsp;<br>Produs recomandat copiilor cu varsta de 3 ani +&nbsp;<br></p>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text text2 pt-4 mbr-light mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle2\" data-app-selector=\".text2, .mbr-section-btn\">\n                            845 Lei&nbsp;<span class=\"cost\">975 Lei</span></p>\n                    </div>\n                    <!--Btn-->\n                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn pt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\" mbr-class=\"{'align-left' : alignBtn == 1, 'align-center' : alignBtn == 2, 'align-right' : alignBtn == 3}\"><a href=\"tel:069371220\" class=\"btn btn-warning-outline\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                            Cumpără ACUM</a></div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
